      Fix seg fault in udiskslvmhelper
      lvm2daemonutil.c: Close FD for spawned process
      bcache_block_check: Fix UDisksLinuxDevice ref. leak
      btrfs_block_check: Fix UDisksLinuxDevice ref. leak
